{
  "id": "adv_event_2112_01_03",
  "title": "胸にしまう寂しさ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――クリスマスイブ前日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day before Christmas Eve",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.8399999619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.6333333333,
      "endTime": 4.2746939023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "明日はのんびり出来ると思ってたのに\n直前になってイベントの仕事が入るなんてなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought we’d be able to take it easy tomorrow‚\nbut then an event job comes in at the last minute.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.488027219,
      "endTime": 11.1376643185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "文句を言っても仕方ないわ\n私達は受けた仕事を全力でやり遂げるだけよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Complaining won’t do any good.\nOnce we take a job‚ we give it our best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.3309977492,
      "endTime": 17.2176643133,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね。お仕事だから仕方ないよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. It’s work‚ so it can’t be helped.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.4176643014,
      "endTime": 21.6118593812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "（せっかく準備したのに、クリスマスパーティーも）\n（出来なくなっちゃったな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(The Christmas party I did all the preparations for)\n(is not going to happen.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7985259335,
      "endTime": 27.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "そろそろレッスンを始めましょう\n明日の本番に向けて精度を上げるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s nearly time to start the lesson.\nWe have to get more precise before we’re doing this on stage tomorrow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.8,
      "endTime": 33.4296952349,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "今日は時間がかかりそうやな\nすみれちゃんは夜遅くなっても大丈夫なん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It looks like this will take quite a while today.\nWill you be okay even if it gets late‚ Sumire-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.6333333333,
      "endTime": 39.6203600914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "今夜は寮の部屋に泊まるから平気だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll be staying in my dorm room tonight‚ so it’s fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8333333333,
      "endTime": 42.571496613799994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "寮かあ……。前は遅くなると、うちか瑠依ちゃんの\n部屋に泊まってたのになんか寂しいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your room… That sounds lonely. Normally if we get late‚\nyou stay with me or Rui-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.7333333333,
      "endTime": 51.487279515400004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "一人が寂しかったらうちの部屋に泊まりに来てもええよ\nすみれちゃんならいつでもウェルカムや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you’re lonely on your own‚ you can sleep over in my room.\nYou’re always welcome‚ Sumire-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.6666666667,
      "endTime": 58.78541219,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。でもこういう時のために\n寮に私の部屋を作ってもらったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. But for this time‚ I had my\ndorm room made up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.9666666667,
      "endTime": 65.20364728919999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "いつも実家から通ってるし\nこんな時くらいは部屋を使ってあげないとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I always commute back to my parents’ house‚\nbut at least at times like this‚ I should use my room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.4333333333,
      "endTime": 71.0754676773,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "本当に一人で平気？\n寂しくなったらいつでも私達の部屋に来ていいのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re really alright alone?\nIf you get lonely‚ you can come over to our rooms any time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.2666666667,
      "endTime": 77.8557633016,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "二人ともありがとう\nでもいつものことだから大丈夫だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you both.\nBut this happens a lot‚ so it’s fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.0333333333,
      "endTime": 83.3499468017,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだよ。急な仕事だっていつものことなんだから\n早く気持ちを切り替えなくちゃ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re always getting sudden jobs.\nI have to move on with it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.5333333333,
      "endTime": 90.42330475940001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "よーし、レッスン頑張るぞー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right‚ let’s do our best in the lesson!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.6,
      "endTime": 93.47036280629999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたの、すみれ\nさっきから同じ所でミスして、あなたらしくないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s the matter‚ Sumire-chan?\nYou keep making a mistake in the same place. That’s not like you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.5333333333,
      "endTime": 101.3547245183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい、なんだか集中出来なくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry‚ I just can’t concentrate.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.5333333333,
      "endTime": 105.9246033032,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "本番は明日なのに……\n早く気持ちを切り替えなきゃいけないのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And the real show is tomorrow…\nI have to move on already…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.1333333333,
      "endTime": 112.037726653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃん\n明日の休み、ほんまに楽しみにしてたんやなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire-chan‚\nyou were really looking forward to our day off tomorrow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.2333333333,
      "endTime": 117.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "うん……私、自分で思ってたよりずっと\n楽しみにしてたみたい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I guess I’ve been looking forward to it\nmore than I realized.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.7666666667,
      "endTime": 124.8534785207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "でも大丈夫！　予定通りにいかないのは慣れてるから\nそれに、アイドルが忙しいのはいいことだもんね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it’s fine! I’m used to things not going according to plan.\nAnd being busy is a good problem for an idol to have!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.0333333333,
      "endTime": 133.4186895965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "頑張り屋なのはすみれのいい所だけど\n無理はしなくていいのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being a hard worker is a good trait of yours‚\nbut you shouldn’t overdo it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.6,
      "endTime": 138.2335941366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "無理なんてしてないよ\nさあ、時間もないし練習を再開しよう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not overdoing it.\nAnyway‚ we’re running out of time. Let’s get back to practicing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.4333333333,
      "endTime": 143.5946793776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "そう……\nならしっかり集中して私の動きについて来て",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…\nIn that case‚ stay focused and follow my moves.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.8333333333,
      "endTime": 149.73333333329998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "うん、瑠依ちゃんについて行くよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ Rui-san‚ I’ll follow you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.9,
      "endTime": 152.5042631149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 153.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～、今日は疲れたなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh* I'm dog-tired.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.5333333333,
      "endTime": 158.86297066999998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 159.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "すみれ、お疲れ様ですわ\nちょっといいかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You worked hard‚ Sumire-chan.\nHave you got a minute?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.0666666667,
      "endTime": 163.6520568857,
      "sfxList": [
