      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 163.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、すずちゃん、どうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ Suzu-chan‚ what’s up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.8666666667,
      "endTime": 167.3932654063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 167.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "イブにお仕事が入ったそうですわね\nすみれがいろいろと準備していたのに残念ですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard you got a job for Christmas Eve.\nIt’s too bad after you made all the preparations‚ Sumire-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.6,
      "endTime": 174.1837606042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 174.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "うん……でもお仕事だから仕方ないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… but work is work‚ it can’t be helped.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.4333333333,
      "endTime": 179.4245803197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 179.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "それで思ったのですが\nすみれの準備を無駄にするのももったいないので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that got me thinking‚\nit’d be a shame if all your preparations go to waste‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.6,
      "endTime": 184.8489611366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 185.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "私達月のテンペストがすみれと一緒に\nクリスマスパーティーをして差し上げますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so all of us in Moon Tempest will throw a\nChristmas party together with you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.0666666667,
      "endTime": 191.0486841072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 191.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルの二人が参加出来なくても\n私達と一緒ならきっと楽しいですわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if the TRINITYAiLE girls can’t join in‚\nyou’re sure to have fun with us!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.2666666667,
      "endTime": 197.3185754079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスは私達も忙しいので\n26日以降になりますが、それでも良ければ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re busy on Christmas too‚ so\nit’ll be on the 26th or later‚ but if that’s okay with you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.5333333333,
      "endTime": 204.3420205829,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 204.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんね。年末は忙しくて時間を取れそうにないんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry‚ I’m busy all round the New Year season‚ so I won’t have the time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.5333333333,
      "endTime": 210.86460336049998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですか。それでは仕方ありませんわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ okay. So I guess we can’t help that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.0666666667,
      "endTime": 216.1375735919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 216.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr020.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、すずちゃん\nその気持ちだけで十分だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ Suzu-chan.\nI’m just happy you thought of me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 216.3333333333,
      "endTime": 220.9355988441,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
