      "text": "落ち込んでるかと思いましたが、平気そうですわね\n安心しましたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought maybe you were feeling down‚ but you seem fine.\nThat’s a relief.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 228,
      "endTime": 234.06242862599998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
