      "text": "ひょっとしてすずちゃん\n私のことを心配してずっと待っててくれたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-chan‚ can it be that\nyou were waiting all along because you were worried about me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.2333333333,
      "endTime": 240.055565449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 240.2333333333
    },
    {
